  <entry>
    <title>利用Hexo和Github部署个人博客</title>
    <url>/2022/07/20/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E4%B8%80/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>利用GitHub和Hexo搭建个人博客，记录生活。</p>
<span id="more"></span>
<h3 id="1·安装nodejs、git"><a href="#1·安装nodejs、git" class="headerlink" title="1·安装nodejs、git"></a>1·安装nodejs、git</h3><p>下载链接：<a href="https://nodejs.org/en/">https://nodejs.org/en/</a> 、<a href="https://git-scm.com/">https://git-scm.com/</a></p>
<h4 id="安装完后检查是否安装成功"><a href="#安装完后检查是否安装成功" class="headerlink" title="安装完后检查是否安装成功"></a>安装完后检查是否安装成功</h4><p>win + R -&gt; cmd ，在里面进行命令输入</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">node -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">v12.19.0  # 版本号</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">6.14.8</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git --version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git version 2.37.1.windows.1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="·安装hexo"><a href="#·安装hexo" class="headerlink" title="·安装hexo"></a>·安装hexo</h3><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">C:\Users\kai\AppData\Roaming\npm\hexo -&gt; C:\Users\kai\AppData\Roaming\npm\node_modules\hexo-cli\bin\hexo</span><br><span class="line">npm WARN optional SKIPPING OPTIONAL DEPENDENCY: fsevents@~2.3.2 (node_modules\hexo-cli\node_modules\chokidar\node_modules\fsevents):</span><br><span class="line">npm WARN notsup SKIPPING OPTIONAL DEPENDENCY: Unsupported platform for fsevents@2.3.2: wanted &#123;&quot;os&quot;:&quot;darwin&quot;,&quot;arch&quot;:&quot;any&quot;&#125; (current: &#123;&quot;os&quot;:&quot;win32&quot;,&quot;arch&quot;:&quot;x64&quot;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">+ hexo-cli@4.3.0</span><br><span class="line">updated 1 package in 17.95s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="检查hexo是否安装成功"><a href="#检查hexo是否安装成功" class="headerlink" title="检查hexo是否安装成功"></a>检查hexo是否安装成功</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo-cli: 4.3.0</span><br><span class="line">os: win32 10.0.19044</span><br><span class="line">node: 12.19.0</span><br><span class="line">v8: 7.8.279.23-node.44</span><br><span class="line">uv: 1.39.0</span><br><span class="line">zlib: 1.2.11</span><br><span class="line">brotli: 1.0.9</span><br><span class="line">ares: 1.16.0</span><br><span class="line">modules: 72</span><br><span class="line">nghttp2: 1.41.0</span><br><span class="line">napi: 7</span><br><span class="line">llhttp: 2.1.2</span><br><span class="line">http_parser: 2.9.3</span><br><span class="line">openssl: 1.1.1g</span><br><span class="line">cldr: 37.0</span><br><span class="line">icu: 67.1</span><br><span class="line">tz: 2019c</span><br><span class="line">unicode: 13.0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>


<h3 id="2·创建GitHub账号并新建一个仓库，注：GitHub-仓库要公开"><a href="#2·创建GitHub账号并新建一个仓库，注：GitHub-仓库要公开" class="headerlink" title="2·创建GitHub账号并新建一个仓库，注：GitHub 仓库要公开"></a>2·创建GitHub账号并新建一个仓库，注：GitHub 仓库要公开</h3><p>创建Blog本地存放文件夹，打开一个文件夹右键git bash here，以下操作均在git下操作。</p>
<h4 id="生成ssh"><a href="#生成ssh" class="headerlink" title="生成ssh"></a>生成ssh</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">usage: ssh [-46AaCfGgKkMNnqsTtVvXxYy] [-B bind_interface]</span><br><span class="line">           [-b bind_address] [-c cipher_spec] [-D [bind_address:]port]</span><br><span class="line">           [-E log_file] [-e escape_char] [-F configfile] [-I pkcs11]</span><br><span class="line">           [-i identity_file] [-J [user@]host[:port]] [-L address]</span><br><span class="line">           [-l login_name] [-m mac_spec] [-O ctl_cmd] [-o option] [-p port]</span><br><span class="line">           [-Q query_option] [-R address] [-S ctl_path] [-W host:port]</span><br><span class="line">           [-w local_tun[:remote_tun]] destination [command [argument ...]]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="绑定邮件-github注册时的邮箱"><a href="#绑定邮件-github注册时的邮箱" class="headerlink" title="绑定邮件(github注册时的邮箱)"></a>绑定邮件(github注册时的邮箱)</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;xxxw@xxx.com&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="在github里添加ssh密钥"><a href="#在github里添加ssh密钥" class="headerlink" title="在github里添加ssh密钥"></a>在github里添加ssh密钥</h4><p>打开C:\Users\kai\ .ssh文件下的id_rsa.pub(公钥)，复制</p>
<p>github里settings-&gt;SSH and GPG keys-&gt;New SSH key，第一个框框随意填，在第二个框框里粘贴密钥。</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh -T git@github.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="初始化hexo"><a href="#初始化hexo" class="headerlink" title="初始化hexo"></a>初始化hexo</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">INFO  Start blogging with Hexo!</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="静态界面生成"><a href="#静态界面生成" class="headerlink" title="静态界面生成"></a>静态界面生成</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo s   </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="令牌验证"><a href="#令牌验证" class="headerlink" title="令牌验证"></a>令牌验证</h4><p>打开初始化产生的_config.yml文件（blog本地存放文件夹），修改末尾代码</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git</span><br><span class="line">  repository: https://github.com/c2h5oc2h5/c2h5oc2h5.github.io.git #你的仓库地址</span><br><span class="line">  branch: main</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>在blog文件夹下 git bash here</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm WARN optional SKIPPING OPTIONAL DEPENDENCY: fsevents@2.3.2 (node_modules\fsevents):</span><br><span class="line">npm WARN notsup SKIPPING OPTIONAL DEPENDENCY: Unsupported platform for fsevents@2.3.2: wanted &#123;&quot;os&quot;:&quot;darwin&quot;,&quot;arch&quot;:&quot;any&quot;&#125; (current: &#123;&quot;os&quot;:&quot;win32&quot;,&quot;arch&quot;:&quot;x64&quot;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">+ hexo-deployer-git@3.0.0</span><br><span class="line">added 1 package from 1 contributor and audited 242 packages in 12.431s</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">18 packages are looking for funding</span><br><span class="line">  run `npm fund` for details</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">found 0 vulnerabilities</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>成功</p>
<h4 id="生成页面"><a href="#生成页面" class="headerlink" title="生成页面"></a>生成页面</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="上传"><a href="#上传" class="headerlink" title="上传"></a>上传</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="再次输入"><a href="#再次输入" class="headerlink" title="再次输入"></a>再次输入</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="验证令牌"><a href="#验证令牌" class="headerlink" title="验证令牌"></a>验证令牌</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">INFO  Validating config</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Deploying: git</span><br><span class="line">INFO  Setting up Git deployment...</span><br><span class="line">Initialized empty Git repository in D:/Blog/.deploy_git/.git/</span><br><span class="line">Author identity unknown</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">*** Please tell me who you are.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Run(注意事项)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  git config --global user.email &quot;you@example.com&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  git config --global user.name &quot;Your Name&quot;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">to set your account&#x27;s default identity.</span><br><span class="line">Omit --global to set the identity only in this repository.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">fatal: unable to auto-detect email address (got &#x27;kai@github.(none)&#x27;)</span><br><span class="line">FATAL &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  err: Error: Spawn failed</span><br><span class="line">      at ChildProcess.&lt;anonymous&gt; (D:\Blog\node_modules\hexo-util\lib\spawn.js:51:21)</span><br><span class="line">      at ChildProcess.emit (events.js:314:20)</span><br><span class="line">      at ChildProcess.cp.emit (D:\Blog\node_modules\cross-spawn\lib\enoent.js:34:29)</span><br><span class="line">      at Process.ChildProcess._handle.onexit (internal/child_process.js:275:12) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    code: 128</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125; Something&#x27;s wrong. Maybe you can find the solution here: %s https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="出现这个错误解决办法"><a href="#出现这个错误解决办法" class="headerlink" title="出现这个错误解决办法"></a>出现这个错误解决办法</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.email &quot;seeyoutomorrow@189.cn&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.name &quot;c2h5oc2h5&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="接着验证"><a href="#接着验证" class="headerlink" title="接着验证"></a>接着验证</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">INFO  Deploy done: git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="按照提示登录-GitHub绑定git"><a href="#按照提示登录-GitHub绑定git" class="headerlink" title="按照提示登录 GitHub绑定git"></a>按照提示登录 GitHub绑定git</h4><p>有两种方式：</p>
<p>一种是网页绑定；</p>
<p>另一种时输入注册时的用户名和令牌，令牌生成Settings-&gt;Developer settings-&gt;Personal access tokens-&gt; Generate new token，按需勾选，复制生成的令牌，粘贴到框框里即可。</p>
<h3 id="4·如何发布博客"><a href="#4·如何发布博客" class="headerlink" title="4·如何发布博客"></a>4·如何发布博客</h3><p>在本地\Blog文件\source_posts里写md文档</p>
<p>然后更新三连</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="5·每次修改要记得三连操作哟"><a href="#5·每次修改要记得三连操作哟" class="headerlink" title="5·每次修改要记得三连操作哟"></a>5·每次修改要记得三连操作哟</h3><h3 id="6·怎么看自己博客地址"><a href="#6·怎么看自己博客地址" class="headerlink" title="6·怎么看自己博客地址"></a>6·怎么看自己博客地址</h3><center><img src="https://img1.imgtp.com/2022/07/18/D7yHNF46.png" alt="屏幕截图 2022-07-18 034728.png" title="屏幕截图 2022-07-18 034728.png" /></center>
]]></content>
